{"tid":734520,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"жғійҖҡдәҶпјҢеҚіе°ҮиҰҒе’ҢеЁҘд»Ғзөҗе©ҡ","createTime":"2018-07-08T16:34:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-09T09:28:35.000Z","uid":76115,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d17d09192b093cc283c5352ec437347fbb1a2930","tid":734520,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T16:34:03.000Z","msg":"жғійҖҡдәҶпјҢеҚіе°ҮиҰҒе’ҢеЁҘд»Ғзөҗе©ҡ<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/736x/4a/35/8a/4a358a084007cdf32bf82f54c68bb09d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2F736x%2F4a%2F35%2F8a%2F4a358a084007cdf32bf82f54c68bb09d.jpg&h=2289c789&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nзөҗе©ҡеҫҢиҰҒжӢјзӣЎе…ЁеҠӣ иіәйҢўпјҢжӢҝеҸ–ж¬ҠеҠӣгҖӮ <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/736x/cb/24/26/cb242629192c4eff09e6f2d3f30649e9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2F736x%2Fcb%2F24%2F26%2Fcb242629192c4eff09e6f2d3f30649e9.jpg&h=88e1f633&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nжңғйҰ–е…Ҳз¶“ йҰҷжёҜе…¬й–ӢеӨ§еӯёBBA(C&amp;G) FT. йҖІе ҙ,е…ҲжӢҝDegreeгҖӮ <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/dc/ef/86/dcef867a9568187f0e0d97309125844b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2Fdc%2Fef%2F86%2Fdcef867a9568187f0e0d97309125844b.png&h=b7802e70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nз„¶еҫҢдёҖйӮҠе·ҘдҪңдёҖйӮҠжӢҝMasterпјҢд»ҘжңҖеҝ«йҖҹеәҰдёҠдҪҚгҖӮ <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/736x/97/70/cc/9770ccd765860a00bd692c8a8c2322b8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2F736x%2F97%2F70%2Fcc%2F9770ccd765860a00bd692c8a8c2322b8.jpg&h=3ce9495b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nжҲҗеҠҹKOз¬¬дёҖжҚ…йҮ‘еҫҢпјҢжҲ‘жүҚиғҪз№јзәҢеҜҰзҸҫеӨўжғіпјҢзҗҶжғігҖӮ <br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/kpop/images/4/4a/Momoland_AhIn_Wonderful_Love_photo.png/revision/latest?cb=20170419100523\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fkpop%2Fimages%2F4%2F4a%2FMomoland_AhIn_Wonderful_Love_photo.png%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20170419100523&h=27e1a498&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(жҗһжЁӮеңҳпјҢйӨҠеӯ©еӯҗпјҢзҲ¶жҜҚпјҢеҺ»е№«жңүйңҖиҰҒзҡ„дәә)<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/kpop/images/6/62/MOMOLAND_Ahin_Freeze%21_promo_photo.png/revision/latest?cb=20180109092409 \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fkpop%2Fimages%2F6%2F62%2FMOMOLAND_Ahin_Freeze%2521_promo_photo.png%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20180109092409%20&h=a1be389d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4е№ҙ Business Law, е°ҮдҫҶе°ұеҸҜд»Ҙз”Ёжі•еҫӢзӣЈз®Ўе…¬еҸёеҗ„еҖӢйғЁй–ҖгҖӮ <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/r9DOy62.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fr9DOy62.jpg&h=f7a05d0b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e93069f7594d3f9710e6b93073fbdfab2d879771","tid":734520,"uid":555,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T16:36:19.000Z","msg":"жҖҘдёҚеҸҠеҫ…жғізөҗе©ҡдәҶе—Һпјҹ"},{"pid":"5df0d5f0974873a564424bca76dd5ecbfc8d6f63","tid":734520,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T16:37:04.000Z","msg":"еҸҲиҰҒиІ иІ¬е№«е…¬еҸёе’Ң жёҜдәӨжүҖпјҢзЁ…еӢҷеұҖиҒҜз№«гҖӮ<br />\n<img src=\"https://data.whicdn.com/images/268560671/large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdata.whicdn.com%2Fimages%2F268560671%2Flarge.jpg&h=43d8cb66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nжӣҙеҠ еҸҜд»ҘжңүиғҪеҠӣзӮәе…¬еҸёеҲ¶е®ҡжңӘдҫҶж”ҝзӯ–<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-frt3-2.cdninstagram.com/vp/8bec092e0b7187890933aea3db327f84/5BA2643C/t51.2885-15/e35/30954006_983466935149987_4397048880395452416_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-frt3-2.cdninstagram.com%2Fvp%2F8bec092e0b7187890933aea3db327f84%2F5BA2643C%2Ft51.2885-15%2Fe35%2F30954006_983466935149987_4397048880395452416_n.jpg&h=4d64e50f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nиЎЁзҸҫеҘҪзҡ„и©ұеҸҜд»Ҙе…ҘзқЎжҲҝгҖӮ <